#: src/Service/RodoTrainingDocsService.php:227
msgid ""
"Report every suspected data breach to the DPO/manager within 24 hours "
"internally."
msgstr ""
"Melde jede vermutete Datenschutzverletzung innerhalb von 24 Stunden intern "
"dem Datenschutzbeauftragten/Manager."

